Requirements: 
    PHP4.22+
    MySQL-3.23.32+ (We test with 3.23.52+)
    Apache

Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://gna.org/projects/blacknova or http://sourceforge.net/projects/blacknova

Credits:
    Blacknova Traders was inspired by many space-themed 
    BBS games (Tradewars, Galactic Warzone, Yankee Trader, Ultimate Universe, and so on).
    but it shares no code with them.  It is
    written 100% in PHP/HTML/SQL/JS.
    Please refer to the DEVCREDIT file to see
    the current list of developers.

Installation:
    Please see the INSTALL file.

ChangeLog:
    Please see the CHANGES file.    

Documentation:
    Please look in the docs/ directory.

Updates:
    Visit our homepages at http://www.blacknova.net / http://www.blacknovatraders.com

Enjoy!
